text: Nabira straisakalara babe te'omlokara pitrbarga, putrasakala, bhatrsakala, bhatijasakala, bhaginasakala, lagara tiraotasakala arau te'omlokara dasa-dasisakalara sanmukhata seya palana nakaraato kono aparaadha nahaya. He nabi-patnisakala! Allahara takbaraa aralambana karaa. Niscaya allaha sakalo bisaye samyaka pratyaksadarsi
